{"tid":792185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：有西方媒體對中國偏見加深","createTime":"2018-08-24T11:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T13:17:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f4d139829ffddb980c523a81ba7f693f5810d6","tid":792185,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"美國新聞網站Buzzfeed駐北京記者李香梅（Megha Rajagopalan），簽證到期後不獲續簽，受西方駐華記者集體關注，駐華外國記者協會更發聲明稱中方做法「不可接受」。內地環球時報發表社評，指是否續簽記者的簽證，是一個國家的主權。<br />\n<br />\n社評中提到，新華社駐印度的三名記者，2016年簽證到期後不獲續簽，不得不離開印度，指出記者的簽證不被續簽，通常有心照不宣的原因，但當這種事在中國發生，就會被上綱上線，形成較大的動靜。<br />\n<br />\n社評又指，西方媒體報道中國的基調長期負面，其中有媒體對華態度甚至越來越激進，有些西方媒體對中國的偏見加深，一些西方媒體人更傾向「唱衰」中國體制上與西方不一樣，但卻獲得驚人成功的東方大國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/3467-b180824-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2F3467-b180824-3&d=4XEq6ua5ntFi6U7Cv1vYxgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=eb6d1648\" target=\"_blank\">http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/3467-b180824-3</a>"},{"pid":"ed7b4dd2542b49f3e9ee27d7d0b5ff8addeceef6","tid":792185,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff9784dac4410c59556c7c618241df6b105bcdf","tid":792185,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"西方媒體=連登"},{"pid":"49c0eacf62b5fc8a3cfb15988d0fb17478a95daa","tid":792185,"uid":73875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"環時咁講姐係西方媒體對中國嘅睇法係冇錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9203d96aab4751f9bfe8056f15fcb16d1d9250d","tid":792185,"uid":166766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"環時日日屌外媒<br />\n屌完扮委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c829f7137c39b4c04118b5fcb96fa81ec02a0c5a","tid":792185,"uid":26506